{"tid":2007276,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【阿嬌閃離】楊受成送上海豪宅做嫁妝 「阿嬌好難嫁得出」一語成讖","createTime":"2020-05-08T08:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T09:28:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c5d76fee52f54dd2cda7b2b4b63d5e558037df","tid":2007276,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:57:49.000Z","msg":"個個都結婚，唔通個個都想結婚咩！阿嬌鍾欣潼兩年前宣佈接受男友賴弘國求婚，除了家人好友戥她高興，最開心莫過於阿嬌老闆楊受成。當年楊受成得悉阿嬌嫁得出，在接受訪問時，連說兩次「阿嬌執到啦」！<br />\n<br />\n楊受成大讚賴弘國靚仔而且有良好職業。當時他說：「我睇佢係好人、又斯文、樣子又好，又有好職業，而且對阿嬌應該都好，見佢咁開心。」楊受成承諾買一對特大龍鳳鈪作為阿嬌的賀禮，又講明會全包喜宴酒席，同時送出一棟市值600萬人仔（約700萬港幣）的上海豪宅給阿嬌作嫁妝，讓阿嬌風風光光出嫁。<br />\n<br />\n可是，由於楊受成接受訪問期間，曾對現場記者說：「阿嬌好難嫁得出㗎！呢次真係&hellip;唔好話畀人聽呀！哈哈！」因為一句「阿嬌好難嫁得出」，結果楊受成被網民鬧爆歧視阿嬌，又指他口不擇言，有矮化女方之嫌。未想到一語成讖！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3itKOK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3itKOK.jpg&h=5ce142ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200508/RTAJHWOGWT53MQ3ZG73G6HCO6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200508%2FRTAJHWOGWT53MQ3ZG73G6HCO6I%2F&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQCWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=f52affe2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200508%2FRTAJHWOGWT53MQ3ZG73G6HCO6I%2F&h=a1a732ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200508/RTAJHWOGWT53MQ3ZG73G6HCO6I/</a>"},{"pid":"37663668daa03fb1ba81b42401b53fa998fec7d7","tid":2007276,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"【郭偉强找數】<br />\n<br />\n呼籲集體投訴社工之恥郭偉强蓄意襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉强社工註冊編號：11071<br />\n罪行：普通襲擊<br />\n<br />\n下載「社會工作者註冊局」投訴表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swrb.org.hk/Documents/complaint.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swrb.org.hk%2FDocuments%2Fcomplaint.pdf&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQCWHaP8IcnP8